    "body": "# Purpose\r\nWe want to add Fujitsu compiler to Spack.\r\n\r\n# List of Changes\r\nChanges of lib/spack/env/cc\r\n\u2026Add Fujitsu compiler commands that\r\n\u3000fcc as C compiler, FCC as C++ compiler, and frt as fortran compiler.\r\n\r\nAdd files to lib/spack/env\r\n\u2026Make a directory named compiler's name, then \"fj\" is an abbreviation of Fujitsu compiler.\r\n\u3000And make symbolic links to cc.\r\n\r\nChanges of etc/spack/defaults/packages.yaml\r\n\u2026Add \"fj\" to list of compilers.\r\n\r\nAdd a file \"lib/spack/spack/compilers/fj.py\"\r\n\u2026This file defines Fujitsu compiler commands and available options.\r\n\r\n# Confirmed operation\r\n$ spack compiler add\r\n \u2192spack detected Fujitsu compiler as spack's compiler.\r\n$ spack compilers\r\n \u2192Fujitsu compiler was displayed.\r\n$ spack install zlib %fj\r\n \u2192I could install zlib by Fujitsu compiler on spack.",
